--newpage Tools
* gofmt
* golint
* go tool vet
* guru `guru what slices/main.go:#148`
--newpage Gotchas
* GOPATH
* Google 'golang' not 'go'
* Channels are great, but don't overuse
* No generics
--newpage Packages
* Exported functions start with capital letter
* go get
